title: Did Republican Dean Browning Tweet ‘I’m a Black Gay Guy’?
subtitle: Twitter users believed the tweet was meant to go out via an alternate, fake account to bolster support for Republican causes.
author: Jordan Liles
vclaim: Dean Browning, a white man who previously ran and lost in the 2020 Republican primary for U.S. House Pennsylvania District 7, tweeted, "I'm a black gay guy" from his verified Twitter account.
